{"tid":399371,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 成功對抗過曱甴/曱甴專家請入","createTime":"2017-09-14T01:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T17:17:43.000Z","uid":1653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bf49437283e379a001d70859c7cadcc79dee7493","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:27:31.000Z","msg":"屌你今朝連續見到兩隻 嚇到我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一隻淡黃色近透明咁<br />\n一隻深啡色<br />\n兩隻都好細隻 係平時見到嘅一半大細到<br />\n係第隻品種定係出世冇耐嘅曱甴bb黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n有一兩隻曱甴出現係咪已經代表有好撚多匿埋咗？<br />\n同埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點樣徹底消滅佢地</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人可以救下我"},{"pid":"1255f39978ebf486b91a4130858fd945233bd71c","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:28:33.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4061b7bc01fe2df9de6c9246851f9118c1b8d0b","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:30:14.000Z","msg":"救我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb38d146eb5c62ad8fc0bdd6cf698eb895a7d76f","tid":399371,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:31:41.000Z","msg":"養貓"