acab58b59a3ffb","tid":399371,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:02:47.000Z","msg":"打甲甴其實最忌拍死佢，因為佢啲內臟會有大量細菌散播係⼂"},{"pid":"edcffdb8f9d3d3f7b054bd84f2dbcb2a4fe9e992","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:03:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Biokill</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好有用？有用嘅今晚仆去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係biokill主要用黎預防，詳細可以上網睇，如果你追住佢噴噴成支都死唔去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該巴打 消滅咗d小強之後再買黎放喺到預防"},{"pid":"daca394fb6892dbed2036bf5fcee3a95cbf1a6a0","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前啲人好推一點絕 <br />\n但我用過功效不大 但可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以買大陸個啲曱甴粉 我朋友用過話勁好用<br />\n<br />\nBtw biokill唔係淨係殺蟲水咁用咩？定係都有效咁滅殺佢全家？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMark低咗 唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一陣搵搵邊到買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e945226fdd00b4d2e6f25ded73bbee5767bbfe","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打甲甴其實最忌拍死佢，因為佢啲內臟會有大量細菌散播係⼂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75532b9540fec3a84c68ff2a8635fe722343a246","tid":399371,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打甲甴其實最忌拍死佢，因為佢啲內臟會有大量細菌散播係⼂</blockquote><br />\n嗱，教你一個方法唔使拍死都可以殺死佢嘅方法。<br />\n首先攞個杯，然後吱啲肥皂加水<br />\n圍住隻甲甴倒水，封鎖範圍<br />\n然後慢慢浸啲水去隻嘢"},{"pid":"3a24507e9a1f23471e62c8f3222554652a8a380f","tid":399371,"uid":38968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前啲人好推一點絕 <br />\n但我用過功效不大 但可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以買大陸個啲曱甴粉 我朋友用過話勁好用<br />\n<br />\nBtw biokill唔係淨係殺蟲水咁用咩？定係都有效咁滅殺佢全家？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMark低咗 唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一陣搵搵邊到買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望你可以快啲搞得掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我明白個種恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓訓下教醒咗見到隻係我張床隔離爬緊真係好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以用下漂白水抺野 曱甴唔中意呢啲味！"},{"pid":"9b496414534827d3e9bf99ff4b3136a0cc2dc069","tid":399371,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一定要用曱甴針,其他果D粉4呀,曱甴屋都冇用,用曱甴針即時見效</blockquote><br />\n咩黎</blockquote><br />\n一支毒針黎，你見到隻曱甴就吉落佢度佢就會毒死"},{"pid":"2417408c24078ac71ad952986fc3b598179ca6ac","tid":399371,"uid":128953,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/101615_fa5941eb86212d3b70c5930cb14ea652.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F101615_fa5941eb86212d3b70c5930cb14ea652.jpg&h=ab537420&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ab3a9e70529efb9cdf8f4576302156d3697326f","tid":399371,"uid":138238,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/101837_a128b5208d650c376b6d63e926abd208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F101837_a128b5208d650c376b6d63e926abd208.jpg&h=dd50a352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\