ass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n棕帶曱甴"},{"pid":"03a3f3efb6bf0e8d64a7ed51bf6ca215c475567b","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你睇下廚房洗手盤底 爐底 或飯枱底 有無 一粒粒好似 紅豆既物體 痴左係度  果啲就係曱甴蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返屋企就check下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有係咪就咁用紙巾執起拎去掉就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88f196393412daa41506b03e465300d0f18de4c","tid":399371,"uid":38241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:26:03.000Z","msg":"近排我屋企都好多，點先可以殺晒佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6e822293e80849178458a7e2449fbcd6ba35e0","tid":399371,"uid":138238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你睇下廚房洗手盤底 爐底 或飯枱底 有無 一粒粒好似 紅豆既物體 痴左係度  果啲就係曱甴蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返屋企就check下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有係咪就咁用紙巾執起拎去掉就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 未孵化果啲就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n你搵支 biokill 係四周圍 隙位 噴下 如果有既 呢種曱甴會走出黎死"},{"pid":"9262cb316fe27543c182bdb5d83831ad3df8362b","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/101837_a128b5208d650c376b6d63e926abd208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F101837_a128b5208d650c376b6d63