1653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Biokill今年已經幫我殺咗三隻小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小強幾時絕種呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔知點解要有呢種生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好核突呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b741b776290a2e628492949299713710160882","tid":399371,"uid":138238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:30:52.000Z","msg":"棕帶曱甴 好多時 因為你地買野帶返屋企的 屋企最好唔好留咁多紙皮係度 因為紙皮有啲隙位 曱甴生左蛋 你都唔知 就會帶左返去屋企"},{"pid":"97cb962283515bd28f0de2200c98e78f2b272978","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一定要用曱甴針,其他果D粉4呀,曱甴屋都冇用,用曱甴針即時見效</blockquote><br />\n咩黎</blockquote><br />\n一支毒針黎，你見到隻曱甴就吉落佢度佢就會毒死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會好難拮中<br />\n如果唔小心拮到自己點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc7ae256618691f120534d4f240b79245553d13","tid":399371,"uid":138238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:32:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你睇下廚房洗手盤底 爐底 或飯枱底 有無 一粒粒好似 紅豆既物體 痴左係度  果啲就係曱甴蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返屋企就check下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有係咪就咁用紙