ets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返屋企就check下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有係咪就咁用紙巾執起拎去掉就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 未孵化果啲就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n你搵支 biokill 係四周圍 隙位 噴下 如果有既 呢種曱甴會走出黎死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你係呢隻品種 好易消滅到<br />\n如果德國曱甴 就麻煩少少啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b4a9e02b94b763e8f071f663010ade56485d39","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:38:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/101837_a128b5208d650c376b6d63e926abd208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F101837_a128b5208d650c376b6d63e926abd208.jpg&h=dd50a352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪咁既樣？</blockquote><br />\n屌 係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌前排我屋企都有好撚多唔知做乜鳩<br />\n殺左一堆未變色既之後好似好左D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好留任何活口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ed6c97e6ffa9ca3970aa6869cc6ec6bfa79a6c","tid":399371,"uid":101618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:58:00.000Z","msg":"去鴨記買甲由屋，$20一盒<br />\n放係廚房d櫃入面<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/105406_dcfa48abffb2057fc40ba161bf9a3067.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F105406_dcfa48abffb2057fc40ba161bf9a3067.jpg&h=ff08c00b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利申用左3個月<br />\n捉左廿隻左右<br />\n再用滾水收佢地皮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9be9cff9ca7b9251b053b7b59694f5c74f9c6fd","tid":399371,"uid":24021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:12:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/101837_a128b5208d650c376b6d63e926abd208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F101837_a128b5208d650c376b6d63e926abd208.jpg&h=dd50a352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪咁既樣？</blockquote><br />\n我之前屋企廚房就係好多呢種曱甴<br />\n去咗買咁隻毒曱甴用既粉 用廁紙裝住放係廚房啲暗位<br />\n一星期左右明顯少咗好多（本身係誇張到打開邊個櫃都有佢地嘅蹤影，放煲粥係到一晚都可以成個煲都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n再放多一個星期就根治了<br />\n<br />\n呢隻真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快啲ko佢"},{"pid":"834e5822714bcb00c9cb6e2e64e9470f7cc54eee","tid":399371,"uid":139193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:12:48.000Z","msg":"淘寶 一點絕"},{"pid":"e384498e7bd20dce8fedff950622106f752d5b50","tid":399371,"uid":24021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/101837_a128b5208d650c376b6d63e926abd208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F101837_a128b5208d650c376b6d63e926abd208.jpg&h=dd50a352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪咁既樣？</blockquote><br />\n我之前屋企廚房就係好多呢種曱甴<br />\n去咗買咗隻毒曱甴用既粉 用廁紙裝住放係廚房啲暗位<br />\n一星期左右明顯少咗好多（本身係誇張到打開邊個櫃都有佢地嘅蹤影，放煲粥係到一晚都可以成個煲都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n再放多一個星期就根治了<br />\n<br />\n呢隻真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快啲ko佢</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1adbdbb5f2e7b39e70d0507e76955d76a334b60d","tid":399371,"uid":82915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8599caca269fe6a6dd3d1b578efaa88199d84dd6","tid":399371,"uid":39369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打甲甴其實最忌拍死佢，因為佢啲內臟會有大量細菌散播係⼂</blockquote><br />\n嗱，教你一個方法唔使拍死都可以殺死佢嘅方法。<br />\n首先攞個杯，然後吱啲肥皂加水<br />\n圍住隻甲甴倒水，封鎖範圍<br />\n然後慢慢浸啲水去隻嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準備得黎佢已經走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 都唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你用d洗潔精樽(有噴咀個隻)入定一樽放係屋企，可以遠距離殺敵。<br />\n我屋企會加多少少漂白水加大威力，<br />\n但小心唔好噴到電器"},{"pid":"cce9fcdefbe55b6cf55866b71f501a61967402a3","tid":399371,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"曱甴針你地可以試下去淘寶搵或者買台灣果款<br />\n簡單黎講一支針係廚櫃底周圍劑D 基本上會死好多<br />\n<br />\nPS.曱甴出沒既地方千其唔好用殺蟲水果D 效果同見白蟻就噴殺蟲水一樣<br />\n結果只會四散,佢地活動範圍會走出廳,睡房果D無殺蟲水味既地方"},{"pid":"da8810dc5617097edfba404e4198869498656ddc","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"唔該晒樓上咁多位巴打 感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMark低晒研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375d5c31858c78efbc24212715ecc3ec1f94a5e0","tid":399371,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打甲甴其實最忌拍死佢，因為佢啲內臟會有大量細菌散播係⼂</blockquote><br />\n嗱，教你一個方法唔使拍死都可以殺死佢嘅方法。<br />\n首先攞個杯，然後吱啲肥皂加水<br />\n圍住隻甲甴倒水，封鎖範圍<br />\n然後慢慢浸啲水去隻嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準備得黎佢已經走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 都唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你用d洗潔精樽(有噴咀個隻)入定一樽放係屋企，可以遠距離殺敵。<br />\n我屋企會加多少少漂白水加大威力，<br />\n但小心唔好噴到電器</blockquote><br />\n大隻冇咁易死"},{"pid":"b155aadd44ded6d1ce5a9005c6db1f50ca80ffef","tid":399371,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"一點絕<br />\n<br />\n用完成屋曱甴死曬, 我落得唔係好多個點, 7日殺唔曬, 但係兩個禮拜無再見到曱甴"},{"pid":"29223f9a6eda5feee130761111b0b8794b63eaf8","tid":399371,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T07:27:16.000Z","msg":"德國甴曱好難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5ae61a4971d3580d045d6f7b41feac458182a3","tid":399371,"uid":14350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0f4ea62ed90fd4cc792a4d5adef30286372fc0","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一點絕<br />\n<br />\n用完成屋曱甴死曬, 我落得唔係好多個點, 7日殺唔曬, 但係兩個禮拜無再見到曱甴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似好多都用呢隻咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下買d小強屋試下先 重有就買呢個試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28137dd115f67e05c66a8a786c88c30a216c443c","tid":399371,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打甲甴其實最忌拍死佢，因為佢啲內臟會有大量細菌散播係⼂</blockquote><br />\n嗱，教你一個方法唔使拍死都可以殺死佢嘅方法。<br />\n首先攞個杯，然後吱啲肥皂加水<br />\n圍住隻甲甴倒水，封鎖範圍<br />\n然後慢慢浸啲水去隻嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準備得黎佢已經走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 都唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你用d洗潔精樽(有噴咀個隻)入定一樽放係屋企，可以遠距離殺敵。<br />\n我屋企會加多少少漂白水加大威力，<br />\n但小心唔好噴到電器</blockquote><br />\n加啲酒精好似仲好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786a1f1d6a962fc9c58f45bbcafaabeb30eaede9","tid":399371,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:06:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打甲甴其實最忌拍死佢，因為佢啲內臟會有大量細菌散播係⼂</blockquote><br />\n嗱，教你一個方法唔使拍死都可以殺死佢嘅方法。<br />\n首先攞個杯，然後吱啲肥皂加水<br />\n圍住隻甲甴倒水，封鎖範圍<br />\n然後慢慢浸啲水去隻嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準備得黎佢已經走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 都唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你用d洗潔精樽(有噴咀個隻)可以遠距離殺敵。<br />\n我屋企會加多少少漂白水加大威力，<br />\n但小心唔好噴到電器</blockquote><br />\n加啲酒精好似仲好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n或者用上面位巴打加我嘅idea。<br />\n用啲唔要嘅洗潔精樽裝定啲溶液。<br />\n水+洗潔精+揀液+酒精+小小漂白水<br />\n當隻甲甴夜晚係地下，立即攞支嘢岀嚟，圍住隻甲甴吱圈。封鎖曬佢嘅去路。水線嘅闊度越大越好<br />\n<br />\n然後就萬事俱備。差在隻甲甴幾時會行動。<br />\n呢個時候我會用酒精噴霧噴佢，一嚟消毒殺菌，二嚟甲甴都怕酒精。<br />\n到時隻嘢會到處亂衝，衝向我地一早準備咗嘅化學溶劑度，呢個時候佢嘅行動會減慢，你可以少量水將佢沖翻去中心，三到五分鐘應該會死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ec744631c3cfc5f7186b244ca8fd470745832a","tid":399371,"uid":4166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:37:32.000Z","msg":"火攻"},{"pid":"f984ced161440a4830a7639ab3b16cb3fcd93358","tid":399371,"uid":42520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"屋企乾淨咪得<br />\n利申:唔怕甲由"},{"pid":"a961cfd44648096dc2256d2c0d4bb200056b0d18","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T15:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企乾淨咪得<br />\n利申:唔怕甲由</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用咗兩個幾鐘將間房用漂白水同藍威寶抹晒再拖埋拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兼掉晒大部分書 紙 再拎晒所有衫去洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望夠乾淨佢地生存唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f466eebf659134b8a11223707edebcb87422600c","tid":399371,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T15:16:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打甲甴其實最忌拍死佢，因為佢啲內臟會有大量細菌散播係⼂</blockquote><br />\n嗱，教你一個方法唔使拍死都可以殺死佢嘅方法。<br />\n首先攞個杯，然後吱啲肥皂加水<br />\n圍住隻甲甴倒水，封鎖範圍<br />\n然後慢慢浸啲水去隻嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準備得黎佢已經走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 都唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你用d洗潔精樽(有噴咀個隻)可以遠距離殺敵。<br />\n我屋企會加多少少漂白水加大威力，<br />\n但小心唔好噴到電器</blockquote><br />\n加啲酒精好似仲好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n或者用上面位巴打加我嘅idea。<br />\n用啲唔要嘅洗潔精樽裝定啲溶液。<br />\n水+洗潔精+揀液+酒精+小小漂白水<br />\n當隻甲甴夜晚係地下，立即攞支嘢岀嚟，圍住隻甲甴吱圈。封鎖曬佢嘅去路。水線嘅闊度越大越好<br />\n<br />\n然後就萬事俱備。差在隻甲甴幾時會行動。<br />\n呢個時候我會用酒精噴霧噴佢，一嚟消毒殺菌，二嚟甲甴都怕酒精。<br />\n到時隻嘢會到處亂衝，衝向我地一早準備咗嘅化學溶劑度，呢個時候佢嘅行動會減慢，你可以少量水將佢沖翻去中心，三到五分鐘應該會死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經整定枝喺床尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一見到就浸死佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}